{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"Docs","description":"Everything you need to know about working with the Ghost professional publishing platform."}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Git","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":null,"toc":null,"keywords":["Git"]},"html":"<p>Git是目前世界上最先进的分布式版本控制系统。记录一些在实际开发中比较实用且容易忘记的命令</p>\n<h2 id=\"首次提交\"><a href=\"#%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4\" aria-label=\"首次提交 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>首次提交</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">  <span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"# NoteBook\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">>></span> README.md\n  <span class=\"token function\">git</span> init\n  <span class=\"token function\">git</span> add <span class=\"token keyword\">.</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">git</span> commit -m <span class=\"token string\">\"first commit\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote add origin https://github.com/jolylai/notebook.git\n  <span class=\"token function\">git</span> push -u origin master</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"修改远程地址\"><a href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80\" aria-label=\"修改远程地址 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>修改远程地址</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># git remote set-url origin https://github.com/jolylai/notebook.git</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote set-url origin <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>new url<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"版本回退\"><a href=\"#%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E5%9B%9E%E9%80%80\" aria-label=\"版本回退 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>版本回退</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 回退到上一个版本</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> reset --hard HEAD^\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 回退到上上一个版本</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> reset --hard HEAD^^\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 版本库的状态</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> log\n\ncommit e475afc93c209a690c39c13a46716e8fa000c366 <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>HEAD -<span class=\"token operator\">></span> master<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nAuthor: Michael Liao <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>askxuefeng@gmail.com<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\nDate:   Fri May 18 21:03:36 2018 +0800\n\n    add distributed\n\ncommit eaadf4e385e865d25c48e7ca9c8395c3f7dfaef0\nAuthor: Michael Liao <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>askxuefeng@gmail.com<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\nDate:   Fri May 18 20:59:18 2018 +0800\n\n    wrote a readme <span class=\"token function\">file</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 回到指定版本</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 版本号没必要写全，前几位就可以了，Git会自动去找。</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 当然也不能只写前一两位，因为Git可能会找到多个版本号，就无法确定是哪一个了。</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> reset --hard 1094a</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"commit-规范\"><a href=\"#commit-%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83\" aria-label=\"commit 规范 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Commit 规范</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://yanhaijing.com/git/2016/02/17/my-commit-message/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Commit 规范</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"格式\"><a href=\"#%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"格式 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>格式</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Header&gt;\n\n&lt;Body&gt;\n\n&lt;Footer&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"示例\"><a href=\"#%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B\" aria-label=\"示例 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>示例</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"git\"><pre class=\"language-git\"><code class=\"language-git\">&lt;!-- header -->\nfeat: 添加了分享功能\n\n&lt;!-- body -->\n给每篇博文添加了分享功能\n\n<span class=\"token deleted\">- 添加分享到微博功能</span>\n<span class=\"token deleted\">- 添加分享到微信功能</span>\n<span class=\"token deleted\">- 添加分享到朋友圈功能</span>\n\n&lt;!-- footer -->\nIssue #1, #2\nClose #1</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"header-️\"><a href=\"#header-%EF%B8%8F\" aria-label=\"header ️ permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Header ⭐️</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>feat：新功能（feature）</li>\n<li>fix：修补 bug</li>\n<li>doc：文档（documentation）</li>\n<li>style： 格式（不影响代码运行的变动）</li>\n<li>refactor：重构（即不是新增功能，也不是修改 bug 的代码变动）</li>\n<li>test：增加测试</li>\n<li>\n<p>chore：构建过程或辅助工具的变动</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>也可使用<a href=\"https://gitmoji.carloscuesta.me/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Gitmoji</a>添加emoji</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"body\"><a href=\"#body\" aria-label=\"body permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Body</h3>\n<p>Body 部分是对本次 commit 的详细描述，可以分成多行。</p>\n<h3 id=\"footer\"><a href=\"#footer\" aria-label=\"footer permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Footer</h3>\n<p>Footer 部分只用于两种情况：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>关联 Issue</li>\n<li>关闭 Issue</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/install/git/"},"timeToRead":2,"excerpt":"Git是目前世界上最先进的分布式版本控制系统。记录一些在实际开发中比较实用且容易忘记的命令 首次提交 修改远程地址 版本回退 Commit 规范 Commit 规范 格式 示例 Header ⭐️ feat：新功能（feature） fix：修补 bug doc…","fileAbsolutePath":"/home/travis/build/jolylai/docs/content/install/git.md"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/install/git/"}}